---
title: Baked Chicken with Corn Flake and Panko Crust and Honey-Mustard Mayo
description: A nod to the kid in everyone! Corn flake-crusted chicken tenders will have you crunching with delight! The honey-mustard mayo for dipping is the only choice for these dressed-up tenders.
